{"tid":1705413,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］第一次全體被罷工，公司已叫所有人返屋企","createTime":"2019-11-11T01:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T00:34:39.000Z","uid":124711,"like":108,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ca6140908471180a7d84f5a15f279ee3c030bd9c","tid":1705413,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:21:54.000Z","msg":"差唔多50個無人返到去，位置好偏僻<br />\n<br />\n一定要黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩最大果粒講叫人全部係屋企等<br />\n<br />\n下晏有機會要返，全體連寫字樓應該有過百人被罷最少半<br />\n<br />\n日，85以黎第一次近乎全體被罷工，香港人還拖！！<br />\n<br />\n利申：老細係深藍，管理層多數黃<br />\n<br />\n所以手足要平安，西灣河果兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班狗已經痴撚曬線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月5以黎第一次全體被罷<br />\n<br />\n放心我唔係作故，有圖但唔放唔自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f915566bd212c38d9c106627d9360edd492b9d","tid":1705413,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:24:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7219edd33dfe15508f442a00edcbb56f8d44109","tid":1705413,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:24:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea87f5e4f7f7aa8adc80a0f35ddc486e975b2829","tid":1705413,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:24:39.000Z","msg":"要keep住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333